Set that there for now.

00:10:53.339 --> 00:10:55.350
And now we're gonna make the spring rolls.

00:10:55.350 --> 00:11:02.779
And these are one of the most fun things to
do with a group.

00:11:02.779 --> 00:11:06.420
Sometimes I like to have--.

00:11:06.420 --> 00:11:08.559
I'll have a spring roll and pot sticker party.

00:11:08.559 --> 00:11:12.029
