00:13:30.699 --> 00:13:35.000
So, over here I've got some really thinly
sliced scallions.

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:36.509
And the chef did an awesome job with this.

00:13:36.509 --> 00:13:40.369
These are even thinner than I usually do them
at home.

00:13:40.369 --> 00:13:45.259
Usually you could just cut a scallion into--.

00:13:45.259 --> 00:13:48.059
Like a chunk of scallion into three or four
slices and it works just fine.

00:13:48.059 --> 00:13:49.209
But this is beautiful.

00:13:49.209 --> 00:13:52.929
So, rearrange it like that going in the same
order.

00:13:52.929 --> 00:13:55.629
And I'm just gonna pick up some of these carrot
matchsticks.

00:13:55.629 --> 00:14:00.519
