carrot matchsticks, the pre-bagged kind that

00:14:00.519 --> 00:14:08.420
you get at Trader Joe's or most grocery stores
in the prepared produce section, that will

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:09.420
work fine.

00:14:09.420 --> 00:14:13.850
A little bit more expensive but if you don't
feel like shredding a ton of carrots it might

00:14:13.850 --> 00:14:14.850
be worth it.

00:14:14.850 --> 00:14:19.689
Then I've got some bell peppers that are gonna
go in the same direction.

00:14:19.689 --> 00:14:26.240
And some cucumber, a really nice substitution
for the cucumber is jicama.

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:39.290
So, then, you just tuck in the edges and then
the trick here is to fold it up really tightly.

00:14:39.290 --> 00:14:43.009
[coughing]

