00:30:42.710 --> 00:30:46.240
&gt;&gt; Gabi Moskowitz: The favorite things to
have in the kitchen?

00:30:46.240 --> 00:30:47.240
&gt;&gt; male #7: Like tools.

00:30:47.240 --> 00:30:48.270
&gt;&gt; male #8: Basics.

