00:31:20.640 --> 00:31:22.610
Good cutting board, good knife.

00:31:22.610 --> 00:31:25.760
Salt and pepper shakers that kind of thing.

00:31:25.760 --> 00:31:28.360
An immersion blender.

00:31:28.360 --> 00:31:32.400
Particularly if you have a small kitchen,
and you don't have a lot of space to work

00:31:32.400 --> 00:31:35.480
with and you don't have a lot of money to
spend, buy a small--.

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:39.960
An immersion blender for 40 or 50 bucks.

00:31:39.960 --> 00:31:44.420
Again, slightly less if you remember the coupon.

00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:49.770
It's great for making soups directly in the
pot.

00:31:49.770 --> 00:31:53.940
Once you start making soups that way, you
will never bother to pour hot liquid into

00:31:53.940 --> 00:31:55.420
a food processor or blender again.

00:31:55.420 --> 00:31:56.880
It's so much better.

00:31:56.880 --> 00:32:00.710
But the other thing is they typically come
with a few different attachments.

00:32:00.710 --> 00:32:03.540
So, mine came with a little chopper attachment.

00:32:03.540 --> 00:32:06.520
So, it's like one of those mini Cuisinarts.

00:32:06.520 --> 00:32:13.610
So, the attachment, the base of the immersion
blender fits on to the chopper attachment

00:32:13.610 --> 00:32:17.140
and I can chop ginger, garlic, onions.

00:32:17.140 --> 00:32:18.140
Anything.

00:32:18.140 --> 00:32:20.390
It's great for making hummus or pesto.

00:32:20.390 --> 00:32:23.880
Any sort of paste-like dip.

00:32:23.880 --> 00:32:25.960
